      <title>我的研究方向简介</title>
      <link href="/2025/06/12/research-intro/"/>
      <url>/2025/06/12/research-intro/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Theoretical-Computer-Science">Theoretical Computer Science</h2><p>我主要关注理论计算机科学方向，包括但不限于：</p><ul><li><strong>计算复杂性理论</strong> (Computational Complexity Theory)</li><li><strong>算法设计与分析</strong> (Algorithm Design &amp; Analysis)</li><li><strong>伪随机性</strong> (Pseudorandomness)</li></ul><h3 id="一个简单的例子">一个简单的例子</h3><p><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>P</mi><mo><mover><mo><mo>=</mo></mo><mo stretchy="false" lspace="0em" rspace="0em">?</mo></mover></mo><mi>N</mi><mi>P</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">P \stackrel{?}{=} NP</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.153em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.1389em;">P</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel"><span class="mop op-limits"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:1.153em;"><span style="top:-3em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span><span class="mop">=</span></span></span><span style="top:-3.5669em;margin-left:0em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mclose mtight">?</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.109em;">N</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.1389em;">P</span></span></span></span> 是计算机科学中最重要的开放问题之一。</p><p><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mtext>TIME</mtext><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>f</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>⊆</mo><mtext>SPACE</mtext><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>f</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{TIME}(f(n)) \subseteq \text{SPACE}(f(n))</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">TIME</span></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.1076em;">f</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal">n</span><span class="mclose">))</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">⊆</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">SPACE</span></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.1076em;">f</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal">n</span><span class="mclose">))</span></span></span></span></span></p><p>更多内容后续更新...</p>]]></content>
      
      
